+### RO-014: Gating Barriers and Human Review Boundaries
+
+Spec sections:
+
+- `docs/specs/rhei-run.spec.md` -> `Execution Loop`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md` -> `Completion Authority`, `Gating States`
