+### RO-013: Failure Routing and Continue-On-Error
+
+Spec sections:
+
+- `docs/specs/rhei-run.spec.md` -> `Execution Loop`
+- `docs/specs/rhei-agents.spec.md` -> `Runtime Semantics`, `Execution Loop`, `Missing Tooling`, `Timeout Behavior`
